### Submit the base64 encoded file

Method:  
 - `POST`

URL path:  
 - `http://localhost:8080/api/v1/`

Input body:  

```json
{"image":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"}
```

Response body:  
 - `HTTP code 200`  

```json
{
    "url": "http://localhost:8080/uploads/6938edb437aa95ce6cf156db2379bde9.jpeg"
}
```
